Package gw.api.web.delinquency

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DelinquencyPlanEventListEventFilterSet
    Allow filtering the DelinquencyPlanEvents LV, based on Delinquency Events.
    DelinquencyPlanEventListEventFilterSet.BeanRefQueryFilter<T>
    A generic query filter which compares bean references.
    DelinquencyPlanEventListEventFilterSet.ToStringComparator<T>  
    DelinquencyPlanEventListPlanReasonFilterSet
    Filters for DelinquencyPlanEvents screens, for Delinquency Plan Reasons.
    DelinquencyPlanUtil
    Handy helpers for Delinquency Plans, mainly to enable UI validations.
    DelinquencyProcessFilters
    Filters for DelinquencyProcess
    DelinquencyProcessFilters.Active
    A filter to return DelinquencyProcesses which are currently executing
    DelinquencyProcessFilters.All
    A filter to return all DelinquencyProcesses
    DelinquencyProcessFilters.Inactive
    A filter to return DelinquencyProcesses which are not currently executing
    DelinquencyProcessFilterSet
    Filters for My Delinquency Process screens that list long lists of delinquency processes
    DelinquencyProcessFilterSet.AllOpen
    Filter to obtain delinquency processes that are Open
    DelinquencyProcessFilterSet.AllOpenOwned Deprecated
    This filter never returns any results because delinquency workflows are never assigned, so it will be removed in a future release
    DelinquencyProcessFilterSet.ClosedInLast30Days Deprecated
    This filter never returns any results because the CloseDate field is never set so it will be released in a future release
    DelinquencyProcessFilterSet.OpenedThisWeek
    Filter to obtain delinquency processes that are Open AND were created within the last week
    DelinquencyUtil
    This class has methods which can be used for DelinquencyProcesses, primarily DelinquencyUtil.startDelinquencies(DelinquencyTarget[], DelinquencyReason)
